22</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">4-STAGE SWITCH - The four-stage switch with various run times: main runs 4.5 hours, sides run 4.5 hours, all run 3 hours, and strobe runs 5 hours. The strobe light is great for emergencies and signaling if needed.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PIVOTING HEAD - The Pivoting head allows for you to shine the light in any direction and  illuminating the sides, main, or all lights for maximum brightness</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HANDS FREE - Ideal for hands-free illumination when you need it. Perfect for emergency preparedness, prospecting, working in low-light conditions, night hikes, and other adventures!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMFORT - There is an adjustable 3-point elastic band and a contoured forehead plate for a snug and comfortable fit.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">VARIOUS USES - working, everyday tasks, construction, fixing cars, camping, hiking, boating, biking, zombie apocalypse, bug out bag, power outage, and any emergency or survival situation</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Rechargeable Adjustable 2250 Lumen LED Headlamp Four-Stage Switch</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">45.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Having to hold onto a flashlight while working is rather annoying, challenging and even difficult. Often you need both hands free for your project. Hanging lanterns don’t work when your head is covering the light. For optimum efficiency, Headlamps are often the best choice.\n\nThis headlamp is best due to the compact size which makes it easy to take on the go working, everyday tasks, construction, fixing cars, camping, hiking, boating, biking, zombie apocalypse, bug out bag, power outage, and any emergency or survival situation. It has 3 LEDs is 750 lumens which combined equals 2250 Lumen. The Four stage switch controls the settings: Main (4.5 Hours), Sides On (4.5 Hours), All On (3 Hours), and All Strobe (5 Hours).  This product requires (2) UL certified 18650 rechargeable/2000 mAh lithium batteries, which are included. This item is overcharge protected, and it takes 7 hours to charge it fully. A micro-USB to USB-A charging cable is included.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
